included.description:
Concept:

There have been times when you call your friends, family, etc. they don't answer their phones. 
At best you can leave them a voice mail, but there is no way for you to know when they will call you back. 

Think of the times when you have been taking a shower, driving, cooking, sleeping, partying, in a class etc. and you have missed calls. 
Problem statement:

â¢ Anxiety and worry when loved ones donât answer their phones

â¢ No way to determine when they will call back

â¢ Anxiety to leave the phone unattended

Research Questions

â¢ Depth of the problem (Pain point)

â¢ Scenarios/ cases where the problem exists (Number of use cases)

â¢ Communities where the problem is most prevalent (Target market/ customer discovery)

â¢ How  do they currently handle this problem (Competition- direct/ indirect)

â¢ Benefit v/s cost of use (Benefit 100 times the cost?)
